{"tid":1024912,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國版「五體不滿足」？　風流無肢男娶嬌妻生4寶","createTime":"2019-02-17T02:44:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-17T05:17:38.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"9558d6febf5ae73820df67086409a558dc1e2e9e","tid":1024912,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T02:44:39.000Z","msg":"美國版「五體不滿足」？來自威斯康辛州的約瑟夫（Joseph Reed），今年34歲。他早在2歲時就因腦膜炎失去雙手、雙腿，雖然生命歷經許多艱難，如今，他擁有心愛的老婆和4個可愛的孩子，「我沒有四肢也能正常生活，我不在乎別人怎麼說。我必須為自己而活，要活得自在。」<br />\n美國《Barcroft TV》13日報導，約瑟夫現居密爾瓦基（Milwaukee），他在沃爾瑪超市的電子部門擁有一份全職工作，平常會幫忙老婆整理家務、照顧4個寶貝，盡全力讓孩子們擁有快樂的童年，朋友們都叫他「無腿英雄」。<br />\n但約瑟夫自己的童年可沒這麼愉快，失去四肢的生活非常艱難，在寄養家庭長大的他，與養母關係並不好。長期鬱鬱寡歡下，約瑟夫也曾一度有過自殺念頭，幸好靠著意志力撐了下來。高中時，他遇上了現在的老婆洛爾（Lore Allen）。<br />\n殘疾並沒有影響約瑟夫的愛情生活。洛爾談及對約瑟夫的第一印象時，她笑說：「這男人是典型的花花公子，跟每個見到的女人調情。」洛爾最喜歡約瑟夫樂觀、幽默的個性，「如果我心情不好，他會想辦法讓我一整天都開心。」<br />\n洛爾坦承，夫妻倆外出時難免會遭遇外界異樣眼光，「我不在乎&hellip;&hellip;愛情能戰勝一切。」兩人結婚13年多，約瑟夫總是盡可能幫忙家務，「他知道如何用吸塵器清理地板，還幫我為孩子們準備食物。」<br />\n約瑟夫最大的遺憾，就是因為身體狀況沒辦法陪孩子們運動。但他自認過得非常充實、幸福，希望自己可以成為孩子們的榜樣，「爸爸沒有手腳都能做到的事，他們一定也能做到、而且絕對不會放棄。」（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190217/640_ee42b477b513683ec8e516cae85e1ede.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190217%2F640_ee42b477b513683ec8e516cae85e1ede.jpg&h=3dba36d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190217/640_076e3c8c0e2616a992bef02dafdf0390.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190217%2F640_076e3c8c0e2616a992bef02dafdf0390.jpg&h=76340690&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190217/640_f120728ff8617ca817084ed15a7afb21.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190217%2F640_f120728ff8617ca817084ed15a7afb21.jpg&h=2aed74fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190217/640_b5dd4953e9b1dab67106c664861d2c0f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190217%2F640_b5dd4953e9b1dab67106c664861d2c0f.jpg&h=d2dff4f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190217/640_568c3cef92a88bfb346a994055b24c68.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190217%2F640_568c3cef92a88bfb346a994055b24c68.jpg&h=17dc2865&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/QDuBYIgOAaw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FQDuBYIgOAaw&d=gHg%2Fa1kZgicCxdd1JZL7Lwx1bwA8BEbsE0NvOM0S0Pc%3D&h=5af3c7bc\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/QDuBYIgOAaw</a>"},{"pid":"18aef6af8a0f89f8ffc9e93de1b281468e50a621","tid":1024912,"uid":46587,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T02:45:35.000Z","msg":"等睇吊住黎屌個張圖"},{"pid":"caa5c781a7f7dcb394d264e705212567e2b74a13","tid":1024912,"uid":112355,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T02:45:53.000Z","msg":"嬌妻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e36d2360adefca671ddbd6d420350db65e32a3a2","tid":1024912,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T02:51:27.000Z","msg":"鬼佬心靈強大，黃種人拍馬都追唔上"},{"pid":"3895d50e43df9d6edc0551c50bb3fcc8833b1a0e","tid":1024912,"uid":25676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"18aef6af8a0f89f8ffc9e93de1b281468e50a621","tid":1024912,"uid":46587,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T02:45:35.000Z","msg":"等睇吊住黎屌個張圖"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T02:53:31.000Z","msg":"呢個size 難啲喎"},{"pid":"6b156779b096f0e6707bc06dde9e5f2792f4c675","tid":1024912,"uid":234235,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,